{"word":"H4310 - מִי - mîy - me - Any","slug":"H4310","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">מִי</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>mîy"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>me"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Any"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05DE;&#x05D9; - m&#x0131;&#x0302;y</b> - <i>me</i><p/>An interrogitive pronoun of persons, as <a href=\"#/H4100\">H4100</a> is of things, <i>who</i>? (occasionally, by a peculiar idiom, of things); also (indefinitely) <i>whoever</i>; often used in oblique construction with prefix or suffix: - any (man), X he, X him, + O that! what, which, who (-m, -se, -soever), + would to God."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H4311\">H4311</a>, <a href=\"#/H4316\">H4316</a>, <a href=\"#/H4317\">H4317</a>, <a href=\"#/H4318\">H4318</a>, <a href=\"#/H4319\">H4319</a>, <a href=\"#/H4320\">H4320</a>, <a href=\"#/H4321\">H4321</a>, <a href=\"#/H4322\">H4322</a>, <a href=\"#/H4323\">H4323</a>, <a href=\"#/H4324\">H4324</a>, <a href=\"#/H4326\">H4326</a>, <a href=\"#/H4332\">H4332</a>, <a href=\"#/H4509\">H4509</a>"}]}